author: djh
msg: Windows build system fix for javahl projects to build on VC Express
and fix dll debug symbols for javahl and swig projects.
* build/generator/gen_win.py
(get_output_name): All projects need to have an output file name
for VC Express even if it is not really built.
(get_output_pdb): Tweak dll debug symbol file name and simplify function.

author: julianfoad

(svn_wc_add2): Clarify node type change error message to not imply that the
next step must be to "commit the deletion", which may have already occurred.

author: offby1
msg: * www/links.html

author: julianfoad
msg: Fix an l10n encoding error for a message displayed when a svn subcommand
takes an inappropriate option taking an argument.
This bug occurs only when using svn with a locale for which translation
for a message " arg" contains non-ASCII characters.  svnadmin, svnlook,
and svnsync are not affected.
Patch by: Kobayashi Noritada <nori1@dolphin.c.u-tokyo.ac.jp>
* subversion/svn/main.c
(main): Don't apply svn_utf_cstring_to_utf8 to strings that are already
UTF-8, partly reverting r9795.
